    <h3>🚨 Nancy Guthrie Kidnapping Investigation in Arizona</h3>
    <p>Authorities are investigating the possible kidnapping of Nancy Guthrie, mother of NBC Today show host Savannah Guthrie, in Arizona. A ransom note was discovered, and Savannah's brother has made a public plea for proof that their mother is alive. FBI investigators are analyzing surveillance footage and details of the ransom note. The case has drawn national attention as officials work to determine Nancy Guthrie's whereabouts.</p>
    <p class="source">CNN, BBC, USA Today - February 6, 2026</p>
