  <h2>💡 NEW IDEAS FOR M2LABS</h2>
  <div class="idea">
    <h3>🎯 "Context Keeper" - AI-Powered Meeting Note Companion</h3>
    <p><strong>The Problem:</strong> People attend multiple meetings daily but lose track of action items, decisions, and context across different projects. Most meeting apps just transcribe—they don't help you <em>remember</em> and <em>act</em>.</p>
    
    <p><strong>The Solution:</strong> Context Keeper is a lightweight macOS menu bar app that sits quietly during meetings, automatically captures key moments, and surfaces relevant context when you need it. Unlike heavy meeting tools, it's passive until needed—no interfaces to manage, just intelligent assistance.</p>
    
    <p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p>
    <ul>
      <li>🎤 Automatic detection when you're in a meeting (via calendar + audio)</li>
      <li>🧠 AI extracts decisions, action items, and important references</li>
      <li>⚡ Quick-search any past meeting context via menu bar hotkey</li>
      <li>🔗 Links related discussions across different meetings automatically</li>
      <li>📝 Generates concise "meeting memory" notes you can share or keep private</li>
      <li>🌙 Works offline-first for privacy, syncs across your Apple devices</li>
    </ul>
    
    <p><strong>Why It Fits m2labs:</strong> Simplifies the chaotic meeting tool landscape. One small app, focused feature set, minimal friction. Perfect for the "less noise, more clarity" philosophy!</p>
  </div>

